code: import http from"../http-common";class TutorialDataService{getAll(){return http.get("/tutorials");}get(id){return http.get("/tutorials/".concat(id));}create(data){return http.post("/tutorials",data);}update(id,data){return http.put("/tutorials/".concat(id),data);}delete(id){return http.delete("/tutorials/".concat(id));}deleteAll(){return http.delete("/tutorials");}findByTitle(title){return http.get("/tutorials?title=".concat(title));}}export default new TutorialDataService();
